data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!!! This townhome has a lot to offer, including 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a large 2-car garage. The bonus room is also a great feature, and it's quite spacious. The property is also located in a quiet cul-de-sac and has a paved driveway.With crown molding throughout, the open floor plan leads to a balcony that overlooks the pool. The kitchen has everything you need, including a breakfast bar and plenty of storage space with a spacious dining room. The master suite has a walk-in closet with dual racks, and the bathroom has a remodeled vanity. The second and third bedrooms are also quite roomy, and the second bathroom has plenty of storage space. The ground level includes an oversized 2-car garage and a bonus area that's perfect for entertaining. The bonus area features French doors with blinds between the glass, vinyl wood flooring and a detailed stone wall. There's also a paved patio on this level. The property comes equipped with a water softener/filtration system, new A/C with Reme Halo filtration, and the garage comes with the "Boat Package" for boat storage. The home is just a short walk from the community pool and spa, making it the perfect place to relax and unwind. The location is also great, with plenty of waterfront restaurants nearby, as well as easy access to the Gulf.
